```

In this code, `Application.StartupPath` retrieves the path of your program's executable file, and `System.IO.Path.Combine` appends the filename `"GeometryDash.exe"` to that path. The resulting `gameFilePath` will point to the Geometry Dash game file within your program's files.

Make sure that the Geometry Dash game file is located in the same directory as your program's executable file or adjust the path accordingly if it resides in a different subfolder.

